(firstQuint)Evaluation of Intra-operative Ultrasound Contrast Enhancement in the Evaluation of Liver Tumors.

 The primary objective of this study is to demonstrate the safety of the use of intra-operative ultrasound contrast (Definity(R)) administration.

 The secondary objective of this study is to demonstrate the improved image quality and conspicuity of known liver tumors using contrast enhancement.

